node.text:
Imagine a problem, a concern, or hurdle you currently have in your life.  That problem concern or hurdle is equal to your current level of awareness (consciousness) as it relates to that problem.  When we know how to expand our feeling inside our body, our inspiration, our joy, we can then become more expansive than the level of consciousness we were holding when we perceived the issue as a problem, concern, or hurdle in our lives. This doesn’t mean we don’t need to address the issue, but when we expand our level of awareness all of a sudden what we once perceived as a problem is now a simple pebble in the middle of the road we simply need to step over. 

Follow @DavidSamuelStraus  for more daily wisdom!

What is your takeaway from this video? Share it with me in the comments below!👇

node.title: How to solve a problem with @DavidSamuelStraus 🧐

node.text:
Your language to the universe is frequency! The word consciousness is thrown about so casually that it’s easy to lose sight of what it means, even more so when it is defined as being “awakened.” Awakened consciousness is a state of being aware that you are aware. It is a realization that you are the watcher, the witness within you—not the analyzer, not the thinker, not even the meditator, but that which is the impartial witness of every aspect of your being and doing. 

Follow @MichaelbBeckwith for more!

node.title: Follow @MichaelbBeckwith for more wisdom on the law of attraction!✨

node.text:
Words from @sylvestermcnutt 

Comment below on your further thoughts! #thegoodquote

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Positive & Motivational Quotes on August 13, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'It is very sad to me that some people are so intent on leaving their mark on the world that they don't care if that mark is a scar. JOHN GREEN THEGOODQUOTE'.

Photo by Positive & Motivational Quotes on August 13, 2021. May be a black-and-white image of text that says 'You need to stop judging yourself based on a timeline you you created as a child when you had no concept of what living as an adult would be like @Morgan.Love'.

Photo by Positive & Motivational Quotes on August 13, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'You don't know why you're exhausted? You're fighting a war inside your head every single day. If that's not exhausting, I don't know what is. UNKNOWN THEGOODQUOTE'.
Photo by Positive & Motivational Quotes on August 13, 2021. May be an image of text.

node.text: Follow @blakeaudenpoetry for more, or pick up his books at blakeauden.com.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Positive & Motivational Quotes on August 13, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Anxiety happens when you think you have to figure out everything all at once. Breathe. You're strong. You've got this. Take it day by day. KAREN SALMANSOHN THEGOODQUOTE'.
Photo by Positive & Motivational Quotes on August 13, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'You lose the right to complain when you turn around and do the exact same. Remember that. FairysForum'.

node.text: Follow @fairysforum for more original and empowering quotes, guaranteed to make your day. 🧚‍♀️

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Positive & Motivational Quotes on August 13, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Always trust your first gut instincts. If you genuinely feel in your heart and soul that something is wrong, it usually is. UNKNOWN THEGOODQUOTE'.

Photo by Positive & Motivational Quotes on August 13, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Healing is a choice. It is not an easy one because it takes work. But keep making the choice and shifts wil happen. YEHUDABERG THEGOODQUOTE'.

Photo by Positive & Motivational Quotes on August 13, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'I don't want to sit aronno and hope good things will happen. I want to make them happen. want to be in control of my own destiny. DREW BARRYMORE THEGOODQUOTE'.

Photo by Positive & Motivational Quotes on August 13, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'It's been said that self-value is giving yourself the respect, understanding and acceptance you give to someone you love. written by NansiaMovidi Nansia Movidi'.

Photo by Positive & Motivational Quotes on August 13, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Never waste your time trying to tying explain who you are to people who are committed to misunderstanding you. DREAM HAMPTON THEGOODQUOT'.

Photo by Positive & Motivational Quotes on August 13, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'You know what, I can over think everything and find a million ways to doubt myself. I've just come to realize that, we're only here briefly. And while I'm here, I wanna allow myself joy. So fuck it. -Her (2014)'.
